
                            OMaze Pre Demo Release
                            **********************

                           Orvo Leskinen 24.10.1996


What does it take to work ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Any amiga with 1 Mb chip-memory.


Why was this pre demo released ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
I need some feed back about the game.


What does this pre demo include ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
This is a 'one level walk through' demo. You can take objects, unlock locks,
press buttons and look around. You can't use weapons etc.


What is the object of the game ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
There are many more or less difficult tasks, you should overtake them all.


How can it be contolled ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
You can use mouse for all the contols.

The control keys are:

                                      Up
                                       |
                 Turn left - 7         8         9 - Turn right



                      left - 4         5         6 - right
                                       |
                                     Down
                                       |
                                       2

                            '.'        Quit
                            'L'        Look
                            'T'        Take
                            'P'        Press
                            'U'        Unlock
                            ' '        Menu


What are the numbers on the top ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
The first shows in which direction you are going: 1-north, 2-east, 3-south
and 4-west. The next two are your location on the map. The last one shows
amount of your free chip-memory.


How can it be installed and started ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Just unpack the archive and click the OMaze icon.


What can one do to ensure that the full game will come some day ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Contact me via Email and tell what do you think about it.

If you think that you are full of ideas and you would like to share 
them with me, please do so.
If you think that you are good map designer, please ask for map-editor.


How to contact me ?
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Email: y95sorle@kotakk.fi
